physical_appearance: The image shows a photograph in black-and-white. It has a black frame and its border is white in colour. There is a single set of railroad that is visible in the image. In the middle of the photograph at its background, there are several tall trees without any leaves. Nearer to the railroad at the foregroud, grass is present as well as trees with leaves.
sgcool_label_text: "This image features the scenery that was seen from the train bound for Johor Bahru. It is part of the ""Tracking Memories"" collection by the late Mr Kwek Leng Joo. The collection captures different aspects of the Malayan Railway story in Singapore
